title: The Pinball Arcade - v1.25.10 to v1.26.11
description:
HOW TO PATCH V1.25.10 TO V1.26.11

1. Copy the contents from the folder "v1.25.10 - Original Files" REPLACE FILES into the game folder 
2. Copy "TPA - v1.25.10 to v1.26.11" into the game folder
3. Run as Admin "TPA - v1.25.10 to v1.26.11" and click "YES"
4. Wait for the patcher to finish (it takes several minutes)
5. Copy the contents from the folder "v1.26.11 - Crack" into the game folder
6. Open the "Resource folder" into your game folder and replace the file "TJunkYard.Rez
7. Open the "Tables Folder" into "Resource Folder" and replace the file "TJunkYard_Enums"
7. Enjoy

The folder "v1.26.11 - Original Files" is included for future patches.


I hope you have great times with this amazing game.
